doctype html
html(lang='en')
    head
        meta(charset='utf-8')
        meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no')
        meta(name='description', content='About Ali Bińkowska - AI Training & HRTech Innovation')
        meta(name='author', content='Ali Bińkowska')

        title Offer - Ali Bińkowska

        link(rel='icon', type='image/x-icon', href='assets/favicon.ico')
        include includes/css.pug

    body.d-flex.flex-column.h-100.bg-white
        main.flex-shrink-0
            include includes/navbar.pug

            // Page Header
            .container.px-5.my-5
                .text-center.mb-5
                    h2.display-5.fw-bolder
                        span.text-gradient.d-inline(data-i18n="pageTitle") What I offer

                .row.gx-5.justify-content-center
                    .col-lg-11.col-xl-9.col-xxl-8

                        // Experience Card 1 - Warsztaty AI
                        .card.shadow.border-0.rounded-4.mb-5
                            .card-body.p-5
                                .row.align-items-stretch.gx-5
                                    .col-12.col-lg-4.text-center.text-lg-start.mb-4.mb-lg-0
                                        .bg-light.p-4.rounded-4.h-100
                                            .text-primary.fw-bolder.mb-2.fs-4(data-i18n="service1Title") AI Workshop
                                    .col-12.col-lg-8
                                        p.lead.fw-light.mb-4(data-i18n="service1Paragraph1") You'll leave the workshop with practical skills. We work on your everyday problems with AI - so the workshop has immediate value for you.
                                        p.lead.fw-light.mb-2(data-i18n="service1Paragraph2") What we can focus on:
                                        ul.workshop-list
                                            li(data-i18n="service1Item1") Writing content with AI
                                            li(data-i18n="service1Item2") Working with numbers - analytics and reports
                                            li(data-i18n="service1Item3") Working with specific language models and tools that connect with them
                                            li(data-i18n="service1Item4") Process automation - we look together where automation makes sense
                                            li(data-i18n="service1Item5") Creating visuals with AI

                        // Experience Card 2 - AI Showcase
                        .card.shadow.border-0.rounded-4.mb-5
                            .card-body.p-5
                                .row.align-items-stretch.gx-5
                                    .col-12.col-lg-4.text-center.text-lg-start.mb-4.mb-lg-0
                                        .bg-light.p-4.rounded-4.h-100
                                            .text-primary.fw-bolder.mb-2.fs-4(data-i18n="service2Title") AI Showcase
                                    .col-12.col-lg-8
                                        p.lead.fw-light.mb-4(data-i18n="service2Paragraph1") Introduction to the world of AI. You'll understand its capabilities and limitations, see what you can actually do with it. I demystify the technology and open you up to new ways of working.
                                        p.lead.fw-light.mb-4(data-i18n="service2Paragraph2") Topics: AI basics, business applications, live demo, ethics and risks, decision framework.
                                        p.lead.fw-light.mb-0(data-i18n="service2Paragraph3") I offer both a short session for the busy, and a full-day workshop where we'll learn the intuition of working with AI together.

                        // Experience Card 3 - Wsparcie na godziny
                        .card.shadow.border-0.rounded-4.mb-5
                            .card-body.p-5
                                .row.align-items-stretch.gx-5
                                    .col-12.col-lg-4.text-center.text-lg-start.mb-4.mb-lg-0
                                        .bg-light.p-4.rounded-4.h-100
                                            .text-primary.fw-bolder.mb-2.fs-4(data-i18n="service3Title") Hourly Support
                                    .col-12.col-lg-8
                                        p.lead.fw-light.mb-0(data-i18n="service3Paragraph1") I offer regular support tailored to your needs - I get into your work, understand the context and help solve problems where they appear. We learn together on your challenges at a pace adapted to the company's needs.

                        // Experience Card 4 - Fractional Operations Support
                        .card.shadow.border-0.rounded-4.mb-5
                            .card-body.p-5
                                .row.align-items-stretch.gx-5
                                    .col-12.col-lg-4.text-center.text-lg-start.mb-4.mb-lg-0
                                        .bg-light.p-4.rounded-4.h-100
                                            .text-primary.fw-bolder.mb-2.fs-4(data-i18n="service4Title") Fractional Operations & Project Support
                                    .col-12.col-lg-8
                                        p.lead.fw-light.mb-4(data-i18n="service4Paragraph1") For companies that need someone to help implement AI in daily operations - not just teach, but be part of the team for a set time.
                                        p.lead.fw-light.mb-2(data-i18n="service4Paragraph2") What I can bring:
                                        ul.workshop-list
                                            li(data-i18n="service4Item1") Identifying where AI makes business sense
                                            li(data-i18n="service4Item2") Coordination between technical teams and business
                                            li(data-i18n="service4Item3") Managing AI projects from idea to implementation
                                            li(data-i18n="service4Item4") Regular support in making decisions about tools
                                        p.lead.fw-light.mb-0.mt-4.text-muted.small(data-i18n="service4Note") 20 years of experience in operational management and IT team management. I understand how companies work - not just technology.

                        // Divider
                        .pb-5

                        // Why Work With Me Section
                        .card.shadow.border-0.rounded-4.mb-5
                            .card-body.p-5
                                h3.fw-bolder.mb-4
                                    span.text-gradient.d-inline(data-i18n="whyWorkTitle") Why work with me

                                .row.row-cols-1.row-cols-md-2.g-4.mb-5
                                    .col
                                        .bg-light.rounded-4.p-4.h-100
                                            h5.text-primary.mb-3(data-i18n="whyWork1Title") Operational experience
                                            p.lead.fw-light.mb-0(data-i18n="whyWork1Description") 20 years managing teams and projects - from 1 to 100 people. I know how companies work, understand processes and know where AI will actually help.

                                    .col
                                        .bg-light.rounded-4.p-4.h-100
                                            h5.text-primary.mb-3(data-i18n="whyWork2Title") Hands-on approach
                                            p.lead.fw-light.mb-0(data-i18n="whyWork2Description") I'm co-building an HRTech startup - everything I teach, I test on my own product. I don't theorize, I show what works.

                                    .col
                                        .bg-light.rounded-4.p-4.h-100
                                            h5.text-primary.mb-3(data-i18n="whyWork3Title") Business mindset
                                            p.lead.fw-light.mb-0(data-i18n="whyWork3Description") AI is a tool, not magic. I'll show you where it makes business sense, where it doesn't, and how to make informed decisions without burning through your budget.

                                    .col
                                        .bg-light.rounded-4.p-4.h-100
                                            h5.text-primary.mb-3(data-i18n="whyWork4Title") Bilingual
                                            p.lead.fw-light.mb-0(data-i18n="whyWork4Description") Polish and English - working with international teams for years. I understand cultural differences in approaching technology.

                                .mt-5.pt-5.border-top
                                    p.lead.text-muted.text-center.small(data-i18n="toolsNote") I work with a wide range of AI tools - from popular LLMs (ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini) to automation tools (n8n, Lindly), vibe coding (Lovable) and content creation (Canva, Descript). But it's not the list of tools that defines my value - it's the ability to choose the right solution for your problem.

            // Call to action section
            section.py-5.bg-gradient-primary-to-secondary.text-white
                .container.px-5.my-5
                    .text-center
                        h2.display-4.fw-bolder.mb-4(data-i18n="ctaTitle") Ready to work together?
                        a.btn.btn-outline-light.btn-lg.px-5.py-3.fs-6.fw-bolder(href='contact.html', data-i18n="ctaButton") Get in touch

